direct - Variable in class vialab.SMT.Zone
The direct flag controls whether rendering directly onto parent/screen/pickBuffer (direct), or into an image (not direct) If drawing into an image we have assured size(can't draw outside of zone), and background() will work for just the zone, but we lose a large amount of performance.
